result.name: Dragon Court Premium HotPot Cuisine

reviews.text:
Worst experience of my life. Terrible service. Plates and toothpicks were thrown at us before even ordering. 
Wouldn’t suggest to my worst enemy. 
My family and I left without food.
Please do not come alone.😂 Big portion if you are alone and craving for steamboat. Good service and fresh ingredient. Non halal
Tasty and delicious Chinese cuisines can be found here. Good and must have a try!

I like the morning dim sum menu. Lies of variety with good combo price. They did not sacrifice the quality for low price. The staff are some good and some not. But once they recognize you a frequent patronage, they will be very nice to you.......the restaurant has two floors with nice window seats in boxes.
Good place for a relaxing dinner in busy mk!

result.name: 龍閣極上火鍋料理

reviews.text: 來香港很多次，卻很少來打邊爐，這間湯底口味還不錯，海鮮也都蠻新鮮，牛肉也都有一定的水準，價錢的部分還算可以接受
食物還可以，但服務員欠缺耐性，態度有點差。
地點超方便，就在旺角地鐵站出口。坐位算舒適，但食物出品一般，價錢不便宜。
新鮮材料靓，湯底鮮甜，冷氣足，時間長!
